headline: U.S. Senate candidate to visit Van Wert
sentences: The Van Wert County Republican Central Committee will welcome U.S. Senate candidate Mike Gibbons to a “Meet and Greet” at 7 p.m. Thursday, February 3, at Wild Hare BBQ in Van Wert.
